<topic id="topic47">
   <title>Database and Tablespace/Filespace Parameters</title>
   <body>
      <p>The following parameters configure the maximum number of databases, tablespaces, and
          filespaces allowed in a system.</p>
      <ul>
         <li id="kh178570">
            <codeph>gp_max_tablespaces</codeph>
         </li>
         <li id="kh178585">
            <codeph>gp_max_filespaces</codeph>
         </li>
         <li id="kh178586">
            <codeph>gp_max_databases</codeph>
         </li>
      </ul>
   </body>
</topic>